title: Now That's What I Call 500 Tracks - 2016 (Part II)
description:
This is Part 2 make sure you grab all parts!!!! Each part has 500 songs!!!

These are high dynamic range MP3 V0 which is better than MP3 320 but with smaller file sizes. Love the music not the file size.

Nearly 8 hours of music spanning decades. Best to create a playlist and hit shuffle. If you don't like a song then delete it! 

This is your music so listen to it like you stole it....


Tune in for upcoming Parts!!!
